WICKED SUPRISE , four wide the first turn, saved ground the far turn, gave way and raced on his left lead in the stretch. LOCOMOTE stumbled leaving the starting gate, was three wide both turns and gave way. C F V NOBODYCARES , a bit rank at the break, faltered and was eased late. Due to a timer malfunction, all times were hand timed.
